    "biography": "<p>A giant Awakened biting fly (Culex pestilans). Females drain blood and Essence and carry a cyclical VITAS-related disease; males attack with mandibles.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Males: Confusion (Zone ×2), Darkness, Enhanced Senses (Improved Smell, Sonar, Thermographic Vision), Immunity to Pathogens, Magic Sense, Search. Females: Essence Drain (Temporary), Immunity to Pathogens, Pestilence (roll 1D6; on a 6 the individual has it)</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Dietary Requirement (Human/metahuman blood, females only)</p><p><em>Attacks: 2L female / 4L male, Reach −2. Habitat: Marshes, swamps, heavily polluted and slow-moving freshwater. Range: Throughout southern Europe. Flying Quickness multiplier 5. 2D6 Initiative dice. Females temporarily drain 1 Essence per wound; the drained point boosts that female's Body for [Essence]D6 turns. Book Body 1/1, Intelligence 1/5. PAE p.51.</em></p>",
